defaultCYCLING SAFETY
default&#xa0;
defaultA coherent approach to transport policy is needed as part of a long-term plan.
defaultThe long-term aims should be to reduce our carbon footprint and to make all forms of travel safer. Increasing and improving 
defaultprovision for safer cycling would contribute to both these aims.  The following issues need to be considered if safer cycling is to be achieved.
