default1. Local maps
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultDetailed maps for cyclists are needed showing clearly which routes provide segregated facilities, which are along quiet roads, roads w
defaultith traffic calming measures and so on so that cyclists can find a route which is as safe as possible.  The maps should be available on
default-
defaultline.   
