default2. The National Cycle Network created by 
defaultSustrans
default.
default&#xa0;
defaultParts of the network include busy sections where cyclists 
defaultare in danger.  These sections should be clearly shown as interim routes and should not enjoy full National Cycle Network status.  Again, this will enable cyclists to make informed choices about their routes.
